{
  "stem": "11641.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I belonged-- personally, I belonged to a group-- also 10 boys under supervision of a man named Baruk Presser, who happened to live in Australia now.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were instrumental in setting up in the factory the ammunition machines-- the machines itself.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Whether they produced or not, that's another matter.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But we setting up ammunition-- the big ammunition machines in the factory itself.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "This was our job.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they-- I understand they never produced a shell that worked, eventually.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But this was not our job.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Our job was to set up the machines.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And it so happened that my brother, Nathan Krieger, one day, we-- I was outside.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I see a group of 30 people coming in.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they was talking about-- and they said, well, Schindler needed 30 mechanics.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they called him in and said, mechanics?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What for mechanics?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They said, well, that's what it is.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And among them was my-- my brother-in-law.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, not-- now he's my brother-in-law.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But he was and another friend of his, Kitchler, who is-- they happen to be both in Florida now.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Anyway, but he-- he came in.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And when he came in, I says, Nathan.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I says, I think God brought you here.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Here you'll be alive-- whatever it is.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Although, we were under supervision of SS, anyway.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Yes, this had nothing to do with it-- not at all.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Every camp was under supervision of-- of the SS.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "The only thing is that Schindler made a deal with them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Don't interfere in my camp.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "If we have any problems, I'll call you.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And that's-- that's-- that's-- this was the main-- main thing.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were there, but they-- they didn't interfere too much.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
